      <title>美联储和关税押注导致亚洲货币指数跌至二十年来最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asian-currency-index-falls-to-two-decade-low-on-fed-tariff-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济强劲增长和当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提高关税的言论支撑美元，亚洲货币跌至二十年来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asian-currency-index-falls-to-two-decade-low-on-fed-tariff-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚太借款人掀起全球美元债券发售热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asia-pacific-borrowers-kick-off-rush-of-global-dollar-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚太地区的借款人开启了今年全球债券发行最繁忙的一周，这是对投资者信贷兴趣的一次关键考验，收益率溢价接近全球金融危机以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/asia-pacific-borrowers-kick-off-rush-of-global-dollar-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国降息次数减少，高盛推迟黄金价格 3,000 美元的预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/goldman-pushes-back-3-000-gold-forecast-on-fewer-us-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，不再认为金价到今年年底会达到每盎司 3,000 美元，由于预期美联储将减少降息次数，该预测推迟到 2026 年中期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/goldman-pushes-back-3-000-gold-forecast-on-fewer-us-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:48:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本最大液化天然气买家成立智库关注市场趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/japan-s-top-lng-buyer-creates-think-tank-to-watch-market-trends</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本最大的液化天然气买家和顶级公用事业公司 Jera Co. 也成立了一个智库来研究国内外能源趋势，以追随西方石油巨头的脚步，在迅速变化的市场中占据优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/japan-s-top-lng-buyer-creates-think-tank-to-watch-market-trends</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 02:41:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
