    <item>
      <title>亚洲货币跌至二十年来最低点，股市涨跌互现：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲货币兑美元的汇率跌至近二十年来的最低点，股市出现波动，芯片行业蓬勃发展的涨幅被日本的疲软所抵消。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/asian-stocks-set-to-rise-after-wall-street-rebound-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 22:31:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊称特朗普的主要立法议程将在 5 月前通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/johnson-says-trump-s-major-legislative-agenda-will-pass-by-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院议长迈克·约翰逊誓言，一项针对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普一系列优先事项的雄心勃勃的法案将于四月份在美国众议院获得表决通过，对于党派分歧较小的众议院来说，这是一个紧张的日程安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/johnson-says-trump-s-major-legislative-agenda-will-pass-by-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 17:55:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达合作伙伴鸿海股价因人工智能推动销售增长而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/iphone-maker-hon-hai-clinches-sales-beat-on-strong-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受人工智能基础设施持续需求的推动，英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的服务器组装合作伙伴鸿海精密工业股份有限公司 (Hon Hai Precision Industry Co.) 公布其营收增长 15%，超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-05/iphone-maker-hon-hai-clinches-sales-beat-on-strong-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 08:25:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
